{
  "stem": "3012.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the little icebox with the ice, and the iceman came and started knocking the ice off of the big, you know-- how do you call this in English?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The big-- Blocks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Block of ice, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you went into the dining room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to the left was my mother and my father's bedroom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To the right was my room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we had the sitting room next to that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a lovely apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except a few pieces of china, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that would have been the least because tangible-- to lose tangible things doesn't mean a thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually, in the late '30s, I believe, they-- Hungary was never a philo-Semitic country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think there was something in the population that-- that's been always anti-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not saying everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would be very, very sad if everybody would be a villain in a nation of 10 millions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gradually, especially when the Second World War-- even before the World War in the late '30s-- they have enacted the first anti-Jewish decrees-- anti-Jewish legislation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Government sponsored.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe that on the university level the numerus clausus-- which meant the quota system, what we call here-- probably was enacted in the late '30s.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, gradually, on the university level, it became the numerus nullus, which meant no Jews admitted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cannot remember the exact date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then when the Second World War broke out, on September 2, I believe, 1939, then, of course-- I must say of course-- Hungary sided with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt-- I felt this in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1939, I attended the first-- my first year at the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
